claim.claim-text:
A hold state change detection method comprising:
acquiring an output signal of a sensor mounted in a mobile device held by a user;
detecting a change in a hold state of the mobile device based on the output signal of the sensor;
judging the hold state based on the output signal of the sensor; and
not outputting the judgment result of the hold state during a prescribed time from the time when the change in the hold state is detected in the detecting the change.
